# 止蝕
(pos:動詞/名詞)
<explanation>
yue:投資或者炒股嗰陣，當價錢跌到某個預設嘅位，就主動賣出嚟限制虧損，唔好令蝕錢嘅情況繼續擴大（量詞：次/個）
eng:stop loss; cut one's losses
<eg>
yue:隻股跌咗咁多，你仲唔肯止蝕，遲啲恐怕連本都冇埋。 (zek3 gu2 dit6 zo2 gam3 do1, nei5 zung3 m4 han2 zi2 sit6, ci4 di1 hung2 pa3 lin4 bun2 dou1 mou5 maai4.)
eng:The stock has fallen so much; if you still refuse to cut your losses, I'm afraid you'll lose even your principal soon. [end of text]


